<script id="wix-first-paint">
    if (window.ResizeObserver &&
        (!window.PerformanceObserver || !PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes || PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes.indexOf('paint') === -1)) {
        new ResizeObserver(function (entries, observer) {
            entries.some(function (entry) {
                var contentRect = entry.contentRect;
                if (contentRect.width > 0 && contentRect.height > 0) {
                    requestAnimationFrame(function (now) {
                        window.wixFirstPaint = now;
                        dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('wixFirstPaint'));
                    });
                    observer.disconnect();
                    return true;
                }
            });
        }).observe(document.body);
    }
</script>

id="comp-jhn2f01g"><h2 class="font_2" style="text-align:center; font-size:42px;"><span style="letter-spacing:0.1em;">DOING ALL WE CAN TO ENSURE YOUR PRIVACY AND SECURITY</span></h2></div><div class="_1Q9if" data-testid="richTextElement" id="comp-jhn2f01r"><p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">Your privacy is of utmost importance to us and your data will always be treated with care.  We are now in line with the new European Union (EU) General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).  In our revised Privacy Policy, we have made it clearer what data we collect from you and what we do with it. We have also provided details on how you can exercise the various rights associated with your data.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">Last Updated: 28 April 2021<br/>
<br/>
This is the Variantz Asia Pacific Pte. Ltd. (“Variantz”, “we”, “our”) Privacy Policy. <br/>
<br/>
We are a corporation registered in the Republic of Singapore with company number 201812772R and a registered office at 1 Marne Rd, The Citron, #01-35, Singapore 208380. For the purpose of the General Data Protection Regulation (“GDPR”), we are the data controller. Our data privacy &amp; protection officer can be contacted at <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#caaebaa58ab9a3a4adabbaa5b8afaba3b8e4a9a5a7e4b9ad" target="_self"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="b7d3c7c7f7c1d6c5ded6d9c3cd99d4d8da99">[email protected]</span></a></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">Variantz collects, uses and discloses Customer Data (as defined below) in order to provide you with a safe, smooth, efficient and customized experience with Variantz. The collection, use and disclosure of Customer Data enables Variantz to provide services and products that are most likely to meet your needs and requirements. This Privacy Policy outlines Variantz's policy and responsibility in relation to the collection, use and disclosure of Customer Data.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">By continuing to use Variantz’s services, you signify that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">SUMMARY</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">What information do we collect about you?</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">We receive, collect and store any information you enter on our website or provide us in any other way. In addition, we collect the Internet protocol (IP) address used to connect your computer to the Internet; login; e-mail address; password; computer and connection information and purchase history. We may use software tools to measure and collect session information, including page response times, length of visits to certain pages, page interaction information, and methods used to browse away from the page. We also collect personally identifiable information (including name, email, password, communications); payment details (including credit card information), comments, feedback, product reviews, recommendations, and personal profile.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">How will we use the information about you?</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">We use your information to fulfill your purchase request and/or our contract of service with you, to administer your membership with our rewards program,  We also use your information to maintain our website and mobile application, and to tailor our products and services to your preferences to provide the best service possible. In addition we use your information to market our products and services to you, and those of our group companies, partners and agents (with your consent where required by applicable law).</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">Who do we share your information with?</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">We share your data with our third party service providers to the extent necessary for them to provide their services such as payment processors and field-operating personnel. We use these third parties services solely to process or store your information for the purposes described in this policy. We also share your information with our strategic alliance partners, other organizations who help us provide our services, related group companies and our overseas stations and with government bodies as required by law. </span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">Where do we process your information?</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">Our company is hosted on the Wix.com platform. Wix.com provides us with the online platform that allows us to sell our products and services to you. Your data may be stored through Wix.com’s data storage, databases and the general Wix.com applications. They store your data on secure servers behind a firewall. <br/>
<br/>
All direct payment gateways offered by Wix.com and used by our company adhere to the standards set by PCI-DSS as managed by the PCI Security Standards Council, which is a joint effort of brands like Visa, MasterCard, American Express and Discover. PCI-DSS requirements help ensure the secure handling of credit card information by our store and its service providers.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">How long do we keep hold of your information?</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">We retain your information for as long as it is necessary to fulfill the purpose for which it was collected, the legal or business purposes of Variantz, or as required by relevant laws. We will usually keep your Customer Data for up to 7 years to ensure that any contractual disputes can be addressed. For EU residents, we will endeavor to delete data within 30 days of a request for erasure or contact you if it will take longer.</span><br/>
 </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">How will we notify you of changes?</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">Variantz will amend this Privacy Policy from time to time and the updated versions will be posted on Variantz’s Website and date stamped so that you are aware of when the Privacy Policy was last updated. Please check back frequently to see any updates or changes to this Privacy Policy. If we make any material changes to this Privacy Policy, we will provide notice including by banner on our website.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><a href="http://www.singaporeair.com/en_UK/privacy-policy/#Updates%20to%20the%20privacy%20policy" rel="noreferrer noopener" target="_blank"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></a></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">General Customer Data privacy policy statement</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">1. The types of Customer Data we collect</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">The types of Customer Data that Variantz collects depends on the circumstances of collection and on the nature of the service requested or transaction undertaken.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">There are two broad categories of Customer Data that Variantz collects:</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• Personal Data. The data we collect includes but is not limited to:</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">(i) personal information that can be used to identify an individual, such as name, gender, date of birth, personal identification numbers;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">(ii) contact information, such as mailing address, phone number, email address;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">(iii) payment information, such as credit or debit card information, including the name of cardholder, card number, billing address and expiry date;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">(iv) product/service information, such as serial numbers, time, location of use, type and method of use;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">(v) information on your other purchases made through Variantz, such as tracking your purchases through our website;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">(vi) your customer preferences, purchases, products that you would like or other service preferences;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">(vii) information about your product or service usage;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">(viii) information about your interactions with our staff; </span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">(ix) information about your interactions with our field staff, such as the details of any complaint cases, call details, and other information relevant to assist our field staff to service you;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">(x) health information, such as doctors’ notes, medical certificates and letters and requests related to medical conditions; </span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">(xi) information we receive from the queries you enter into our chatbot and Website (as defined below);<br/>
<br/>
(xii) information we receive from product and/or service bookings made via our online corporate booking platform; <br/>
<br/>
(xiii) information we receive from other sources e.g. our page on social media websites; and<br/>
<br/>
(xiv) business contact information, such as the contact details of the employees of our vendors and corporate customers, as well as the contact details collected by our divisions.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• Technical Data. This includes device and technical information you give us when using our website or mobile application (“Website”) such as IP addresses or other unique identifiers, cookies, mobile carrier, time zone setting, operating system and platform. Information on cookies may be found in our <a href="http://www.singaporeair.com/en_UK/global_footer/cookies-policy/" rel="noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">cookie policy.</a></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">For purposes of this policy statement, Customer Data means Personal Data and Technical Data.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">We also use Customer Data to derive Statistical Data, such as the number of subscribers. This is processed and stored purely for analytical purposes, and is entirely anonymous. This information will not be stored to your customer record, and will only be aggregated for statistical analysis so that we can better understand Variantz's customer profile and improve Variantz's service offering.</span><br/>
 </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span style="text-decoration:underline;">Special categories of information or “sensitive personal data”</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">Certain categories of Customer Data, such as information about your race, ethnicity, religion or health, are considered special categories of information, or “sensitive personal data” under the GDPR.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">Generally, we try to limit the circumstances where we collect your sensitive personal data. However, this can occasionally occur because you have made certain requests in connection with your service arrangements that reveal or suggest something about you that could be considered “sensitive personal data”, or if you otherwise choose to provide such information to us.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">For example:</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• if you request a particular type of feature, e.g. Muslim prayer time, this may imply or suggest that you are a member of a particular religion; or</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• if you request specific medical assistance from us and/or an operator, e.g. the provision of a wheelchair, this may reveal that you have a particular medical condition.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">How we collect data from you</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">Variantz collects Customer Data, either directly from you or from your authorized representatives (i.e. persons whom you have authorized and/or persons who have been validly identified as being your authorized representative (e.g. your organisation’s corporate service manager) pursuant to our then-current security procedures).</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">Variantz also collects Customer Data from third parties which are located in various countries. This includes, but is not limited to, our Variantz partners, our service providers, including our subsidiaries, or through our Website, mobile services, any posts on our Variantz-specific pages on social media websites and other channels including our service counters and retail operations.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">Where you conduct a transaction on our website, as part of the process, and/or make transactions on behalf of another person, you undertake and will ensure that the individual whose Customer Data is supplied to Variantz has authorized the disclosure, is informed of and agrees to the provisions of this Privacy Policy.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">2. Is the provision of Customer Data required?</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">The collection of the following types of Customer Data is mandatory to enable Variantz to fulfill our contract of service with you. These types of Customer Data are marked as mandatory on our booking form. If you do not provide this information, we will not be able to provide you with our services and/or products required.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• User details, e.g title, first/given name, last/family name, date of birth, whether you are an EU resident.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• Contact details, e.g. email address, mobile phone number, home number or business number.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• Payment details, e.g. the name on the credit or debit card, the credit or debit card number, expiry date and card verification value on the credit or debit card, and billing address which will be transmitted to our payments processors.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">Additional information may be mandatory if you are using the product/service in a specific country, or if you are using the product/service on behalf of a business registered in a specific country, e.g. your gender, nationality, passport number, the country of issue of your passport, the name, GST registration number and address of the business you are using on behalf of, and your business email address and phone number.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">These types of Customer Data are marked as mandatory on our sign up form. If you do not provide this information, you will not be able to benefit from points accruals and membership tier benefits and we will not be able to provide you with our services and/or products required.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">The failure to supply the following types of Customer Data will result in (i) Variantz being unable to update you on our latest products and/or launches; and/or (ii) your inability to enter or participate in contests, promotions or redemption activities organised by Variantz:</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• Contact Information e.g. email address, telephone number; and<br/>
<br/>
• Country of residence.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">3. How we use your Customer Data</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">If you are an EU resident, we are required to disclose the legal basis for processing your data under the GDPR. We will use the Customer Data in the following ways:</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">In accordance with our contract of service with you, we will use the Customer Data to:</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• process and assist you with any transactions related to your service, fulfilling such booking and investigating potential fraudulent transactions);</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• notify you about changes to our service, including through service alert messages via Variantz’s mobile services facility;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• provide services (e.g. to provide you with a personalized application experience);</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">iv. Send you membership status updates and other account related information.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">As it is in our legitimate interests to be responsive to you, to provide customised services and marketing and to ensure the proper functioning of our products, services and organisation, we will use your Customer Data to:</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• improve the Website and to ensure content from the Website is presented in the most effective manner for you and your device;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• administer the Website and for internal operations, including troubleshooting, data analysis, testing, research, statistical and survey purposes;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• monitor and record calls for quality, training, legal compliance, analysis and other related purposes in order to pursue our legitimate interest to improve service delivery;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• send you surveys by email. You can opt-out of receiving these surveys at any time by contacting us;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• send you service emails, such as reminders when you have not checked out your purchases on our Website. You can opt-out of receiving service emails at any time by contacting us;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• respond to your enquiries, requests or feedback;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• enforce our terms, conditions and policies;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• allow you to participate in interactive features of the Website, when you choose to do so;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• customise our products and services to you, including by responding to and catering for your customer preferences;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• personalize the content you see on our Website and on our infotainment systems, by enabling you to save your preferences on our infortainment systems;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• keep the Website safe and secure;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• aggregate Customer Data into anonymized statistical data (such as number of users using a particular feature), which we will use for statistical analysis so that we can better understand Variantz's customer profile and improve Variantz's service offering;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• to customize our marketing e.g. send you targeted marketing on places you would like to visit, based on your responses to optional questions on our Website and your prior purchases. </span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">If you are an EU resident, you can object to this profiling and opt-out of receiving such targeted marketing. </span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">With your consent where required by applicable laws, we will use your Customer Data to:</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• send you marketing and promotional materials in relation to products and services offered by Variantz, Variantz’s subsidiaries and affiliate and service partners, as well as Variantz's appointed agents.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">You have the right to withdraw your consent at any time by contacting us at <a data-auto-recognition="true" href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#07637777477166756e6669737d2964686a"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="b3d7c3c3f3c5d2c1dad2ddc7c99dd0dcde">[email protected]</span></a>.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">4. Disclosure of your Customer Data</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">Variantz will share your Customer Data with selected third parties in the situations set out below:</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• our service providers (including field personnel, security personnel and providers of infotainment and internet connection);</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• our strategic alliance partners so that they can fulfill their contract of service you booked through Variantz. Where Customer Data is shared with such partners, the Customer Data will be used by that partner in accordance with their respective privacy policy.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• advertisers and advertising networks that require the data to select and serve relevant adverts to you and others;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• analytics and search engine providers that assist us in the improvement and optimisation of the Website.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">Variantz will share your Customer Data with any member of our group, which means our overseas stations and our subsidiaries  in order to better customise your preferences:</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• For the purposes of our contract with you, i.e. to:</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">i. Fulfill purchases of product/service and facilitate provisioning of product/service;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">ii. Manage customers from our subsidiaries or partners;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">iii. Manage customers during service disruptions and provide necessary assistance and services;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• As it is in our legitimate interests to be responsive to you, to provide customised services and marketing, to:</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">i. Respond to complaints or compliments received by Variantz from customers who are sharing their service experience operated by our subsidiaries;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">ii. Providing an enhanced customer experience and personalizing offers to customers;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">iii. Anticipating the servicing needs of customers;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:80px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">iv. Understanding customers better through analytics and research (including marketing research) to support personalisation;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• For the purposes of undertaking targeted direct marketing and other forms of marketing or advertisement, provided we have the consent of the recipient and/or have provided the opportunity to opt-out, in each case where required by applicable law. Variantz will also use and disclose your Customer Data to persons who have been validly identified as being you or your authorized representative(s) pursuant to our then-current security procedures, for the purpose of the relevant transaction or inquiry. In particular, each of the customer who are grouped under the same Customer Name Record (“CNR”) number shall be deemed to be authorized representatives of each of the other passengers under the same PNR number. Variantz will disclose your Customer Data to law enforcement agencies, public or regulatory authorities, securities commissions or other organisations for security, customs and law enforcement purposes, if legally required to do so, or if we have a good faith belief that such use is reasonably necessary to:</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• comply with legal obligation, process or request;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• enforce our terms and conditions and other agreements, including investigation of any potential violation thereof;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• detect, prevent or otherwise address security, fraud or technical issues; or</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• protect the rights, property, health or safety of us, our users, a third party or the public as required or permitted by law (including exchanging Customer Data with other companies and organisations for the purposes of fraud protection and credit risk reduction). <br/>
<br/>
We will also disclose your Customer Data to third parties:</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• in the event that we sell or buy any business or assets, in which case we may disclose your data to the prospective seller or buyer of such business or assets;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• if we or substantially all of our assets are acquired by a third party, in which case Customer Data held by us about our customers will be one of the transferred assets; or</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• to comply with legal obligations, processes or requests (such as disclosing Customer Data to executors in response to court orders). <br/>
<br/>
In addition, Variantz may disclose Customer Data to our legal advisors for establishing, exercising or defending our legal rights, to our other professional advisors, or as otherwise authorised or required by law. Variantz also reserves the right to share Customer Data as is necessary to prevent a threat to the life, health or security of an individual or corporate entities such as Variantz. Further, Variantz will disclose Customer Data, as is necessary, to investigate suspected unlawful activities including but not limited to fraud, intellectual property infringement or privacy.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">5. Transfer of information overseas</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">The Variantz Head Office is based in Singapore. Our company is hosted on the Wix.com platform. Wix.com provides us with the online platform that allows us to sell our products and services to you. Your data may be stored through Wix.com’s data storage, databases and the general Wix.com applications. They store your data on secure servers behind a firewall.  Customer Data will be transferred to Variantz's offices and appointed agents, including field agents, sales agents and contact center agents, in Singapore and around the world in connection with Variantz’s performance of the contract with you.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">This means that Customer Data will be transferred to, and stored at, a destination outside of your country and outside the European Economic Area ("EEA").  We will transfer Customer Data to destinations that you are using the service in and where we operate. The Customer Data is transferred outside the EEA on the basis that it is necessary for the performance of the contract of seervice between you and Variantz. </span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">We will also transfer Customer Data to our partners in strategic alliances in  Europe, West Asia and Africa, North Asia, Southeast Asia, Southwest Pacific and the Americas for the purposes of performing any contract of service. <br/>
<br/>
If you are an EU resident, where we transfer Customer Data outside the EEA, this is done either on the basis that it is necessary for the performance of the contract of service between you and Variantz, or that the transfer is subject to the European Commission’s model contracts for the transfer of personal data to third countries (i.e., the standard contractual clauses), pursuant to Decision 2004/915/EC and Decision 2010/87/EU as appropriate.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">The Customer Data will also be processed by staff operating outside the EEA who work for us, for our suppliers or our business partners. Such staff are engaged in, among other things, the fulfilment of your order, the processing of your payment details and the provision of support services.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">6. Non-EU Data Subject Rights</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">If you are not a resident in the EU, you may have certain rights in relation to the Customer Data we hold about you, which we detail below.<br/>
<br/>
<span style="text-decoration:underline;">Access.</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">You have the right to know whether we process Customer Data about you, and if we do, to access Customer Data we hold about you and certain information about how we use it and who we share it with.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">Where permitted by law, Variantz reserves the right to charge a reasonable administrative fee for this service. In exceptional circumstances, Variantz reserves the right to deny you access to your Customer Data and may provide an explanation as required by applicable laws.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">Exceptional circumstances include (to the extent allowable under applicable law) where:</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• an investigating authority or government institution objects to Variantz complying with a customer’s request;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• the information may, in the exercise of Variantz’s reasonable discretion and/or assessment, affect the life or security of an individual; and</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• data is collected in connection with an investigation of a breach of contract, suspicion of fraudulent activities or contravention of law.</span><br/>
 </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span style="text-decoration:underline;">Correction</span> <br/>
You have the right to correct any Customer Data held about you that is inaccurate.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span style="text-decoration:underline;">Feedback and complaints</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">If you have any concerns, feedback or complaints about the use and/or sharing of your Customer Data, we are open to receiving your feedback or complaints.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span style="text-decoration:underline;">Exercise of Rights.</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">To exercise any of your rights, please go to "Contact Us" for instructions.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">7. EU Data Subject Rights</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">If you are a resident in the EU, you may have certain rights in relation to the Customer Data we hold about you, which we detail below. Some of these only apply in certain circumstances as set out in more detail below. We also set out how to exercise those rights.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">These rights include:</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• The right of access.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• The right of data portability. </span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• The right of rectification. </span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• The right of erasure. </span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• The right to restrict processing. </span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• The right to object. </span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">Please note that we will require you to provide us with proof of identity before responding to any requests to exercise your rights. We must respond to a request by you to exercise those rights without undue delay and at least within one month (although this may be extended by a further two months in certain circumstances). To exercise any of your rights, please go to "Contact Us" for instructions.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span style="text-decoration:underline;">Complaints.</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">In the event that you wish to make a complaint about how we process your Customer Data, please contact us and we will endeavour to deal with your request as soon as possible. This is without prejudice to your right to launch a claim with your data protection authority.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span style="text-decoration:underline;">Access.</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">You have the right to know whether we process Customer Data about you, and if we do, to access Customer Data we hold about you and certain information about how we use it and who we share it with.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">If you require more than one copy of the Customer Data we hold about you, we may charge an administration fee.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">We may not provide you with certain Customer Data if providing it would interfere with another’s rights (e.g. where providing the Customer Data we hold about you would reveal information about another person) or where another exemption applies.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span style="text-decoration:underline;">Portability.</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">You have the right to receive a subset of the Customer Data we collect from you in a structured, commonly used and machine-readable format and a right to request that we transfer such Customer Data to another party.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">If you wish for us to transfer the Customer Data to another party, please ensure you detail that party and note that we can only do so where it is technically feasible. We are not responsible for the security of the Customer Data or its processing once received by the third party. We also may not provide you with certain Customer Data if providing it would interfere with another’s rights (e.g. where providing the Customer Data we hold about you would reveal information about another person). </span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span style="text-decoration:underline;">Correction.</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">You have the right to correct any Customer Data held about you that is inaccurate. Please note that whilst we assess whether the Customer Data we hold about you is inaccurate or incomplete, you may exercise your right to restrict our processing of the applicable data as described below.</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span style="text-decoration:underline;">Erasure.</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">You may request that we erase the Customer Data we hold about you in the following circumstances:</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• you believe that it is no longer necessary for us to hold the Customer Data we hold about you;</span></p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"> </p>
<p class="font_8" style="margin-left:40px; text-align:justify; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_71196e_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de07530521,wf_82cc4b6b949046d98b5963de0,orig_contax_w_01_45_light;">• we are processing the Customer Data we hold about you on the basis of your consent (please see here for the types of Customer Data we process on the basis of your consent, and you wish to withdraw your consent and there is no other ground under which we can process the Customer Data;</span></p>
